    <para id="fs-id1174050">The energy falling on the solar collector in 4 h in part is enough to be useful—for example, for heating a significant amount of water.</para>
    <para id="import-auto-id1157183"><title>Strategy b</title></para>
    <para id="fs-id3077951">Taking a ratio of new intensity to old intensity and using primes for the new quantities, we will find that it depends on the ratio of the areas. All other quantities will cancel.</para>
